      <div class="about-main-card">
        <p>MyTaxCalcs is a free tax calculator website designed to help users estimate common U.S. tax situations, including federal income tax, state income tax, self-employment tax, sales tax, capital gains tax, payroll tax, and tax refund estimates.</p>

        <h2>Our goal</h2>
        <p>The goal of MyTaxCalcs is to make tax estimates easier to understand. Instead of only showing a final number, our calculators are designed to show taxable income, deductions, estimated tax, withholding, refunds, and amount owed in a simple, clear format.</p>

        <h2>What MyTaxCalcs does not do</h2>
        <p>MyTaxCalcs does not provide tax, legal, accounting, or financial advice. Tax rules can change, and every taxpayer's situation is different. Always verify results with official tax sources or a qualified tax professional.</p>

        <h2>Current calculators</h2>
        <p>The site currently includes a federal income tax calculator, tax refund calculator, self-employment tax calculator, capital gains tax calculator, sales tax calculator, payroll tax calculator, and state income tax calculator pages for all 50 U.S. states.</p>

